{"tid":791152,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"(budget 3萬內) 錶","createTime":"2018-08-23T14:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T11:26:24.000Z","uid":194192,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"9e04caa60e63b5ff1724ba7030f4734f8b1d1587","tid":791152,"uid":194192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"各位巴打 近排想買隻錶 budget 3萬內 想問下大家意見<br />\n<br />\n我心水暫時有兩隻 <br />\n<br />\n－Omega Speedmaster Moonwatch Professional <br />\n<br />\n－Tudor Black Bay Chrono<br />\n<br />\nSpeedmaster 個隻比較經典 時間耐咗都好襟睇 襯皮帶都好靚 但比較低調<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/222339_4e0c71ab25ef8334dfea8e9aa91ef0e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F222339_4e0c71ab25ef8334dfea8e9aa91ef0e7.jpg&h=9e3f2eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/222339_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F222339_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=475382a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTudor 個隻breitling機芯 鍾意錶面比較多detail 但配snowflake hands 感覺有d 奇怪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/222338_45e6bebdc9ae9040c169c9803393f29f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F222338_45e6bebdc9ae9040c169c9803393f29f.jpg&h=5ae34a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/222339_3103f33431676834fd37e752f7efe146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F222339_3103f33431676834fd37e752f7efe146.jpg&h=2026e342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位對呢兩隻有咩意見 或者有冇其他錶推介下 thanks！"},{"pid":"b3d75a015ccf9a0bd3eeff56ba696daed018f221","tid":791152,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":